# End-to-End RFI Agent Workflow

## Overview

The objective of the RFI Agent is to assist Operational Risk Control Testing by analyzing structured control testing requests, identifying missing information, reasoning over potential gaps, and preparing a human-reviewable Request For Information (RFI).

The implementation follows a modular AI pipeline where each component has a single responsibility. This architecture promotes explainability, maintainability, and extensibility, allowing each phase to evolve independently while preserving the overall workflow.

Unlike a monolithic AI assistant, the solution decomposes the RFI lifecycle into specialized reasoning components.

